<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>Tests</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">All<sp/>logical<sp/>game-related<sp/>and<sp/>data-related<sp/>tests<sp/>are<sp/>found<sp/>here.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Their<sp/>purpose<sp/>is<sp/>to<sp/>test<sp/>the<sp/>inner<sp/>functionalities<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>game<sp/>and<sp/>the<sp/>existence<sp/>of<sp/>files<sp/>used<sp/>by<sp/>it.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Unit<sp/>tests<sp/>are<sp/>found<sp/>under<sp/>the<sp/>`unit/`<sp/>directory,<sp/>integrated<sp/>tests<sp/>are<sp/>found<sp/>under<sp/>the<sp/>`integrated/`<sp/>directory.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Running<sp/>a<sp/>test</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Install<sp/>the<sp/>required<sp/>dependencies<sp/>using<sp/>(run<sp/>in<sp/>root<sp/>dir):</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```bash</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">pip<sp/>install<sp/>-e<sp/>.[test_modules]</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">If<sp/>you<sp/>want,<sp/>position<sp/>yourself<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>`tests`<sp/>directory<sp/>using:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```bash</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">cd<sp/>tests</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>To<sp/>run<sp/>all<sp/>tests:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```bash</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">pytest<sp/>.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>To<sp/>run<sp/>all<sp/>tests<sp/>of<sp/>a<sp/>certain<sp/>type:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
